{
  "app": {
    "title": "City Planner",
    "primaryColor": "#2E7D32",
    "theme": "material",
    "autosave": true
  },
  "nav": [
    {
      "id": "map",
      "label": "Map",
      "icon": "map",
      "screen": "map"
    },
    {
      "id": "stats",
      "label": "Stats",
      "icon": "insights",
      "screen": "stats"
    },
    {
      "id": "residents",
      "label": "Residents",
      "icon": "person",
      "screen": "residents"
    },
    {
      "id": "guide",
      "label": "How to play",
      "icon": "help_outline",
      "screen": "guide"
    }
  ],
  "screens": {
    "map": {
      "title": "City Planner",
      "body": {
        "type": "column",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "style": "caption",
            "value": "Zone the lots, then end the turn. Residents' happiness rises with good, affordable groceries, schools, healthcare, parks, walkability and transit — and falls with pollution, car dependence and high grocery prices. Tap a pin to set its zone (and quality/cost for groceries, schools, hospitals)."
          },
          {
            "type": "table",
            "table": "city",
            "columns": [
              "turn",
              "budget",
              "population",
              "happiness"
            ],
            "height": 96
          },
          {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "End turn",
            "icon": "skip_next",
            "action": {
              "fn": "endTurn",
              "args": {
                "state": "city",
                "stateId": "s1",
                "units": "parcels",
                "turnField": "turn",
                "tallies": {
                  "res": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "residential"
                  },
                  "com": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "commercial"
                  },
                  "ind": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "industrial"
                  },
                  "park": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "park"
                  },
                  "grocery": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "grocery"
                  },
                  "school": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "school"
                  },
                  "hospital": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "hospital"
                  },
                  "transit": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "transit"
                  },
                  "schoolQual": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "school",
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  },
                  "hospitalQual": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "hospital",
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  },
                  "groceryQual": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "grocery",
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  },
                  "groceryCostAvg": {
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "grocery",
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "cost"
                  }
                },
                "effects": [
                  {
                    "field": "budget",
                    "mode": "add",
                    "base": -5,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "com",
                        "coef": 12
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "res",
                        "coef": 4
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "ind",
                        "coef": 9
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "grocery",
                        "coef": 5
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "park",
                        "coef": -2
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "school",
                        "coef": -5
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "hospital",
                        "coef": -7
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "transit",
                        "coef": -4
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "population",
                    "mode": "add",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "res",
                        "coef": 25
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "pollution",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "ind",
                        "coef": 6
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "com",
                        "coef": 1
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "park",
                        "coef": -2
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "transit",
                        "coef": -1
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "walkability",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 10,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "park",
                        "coef": 4
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "grocery",
                        "coef": 5
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "transit",
                        "coef": 6
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "school",
                        "coef": 3
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "ind",
                        "coef": -2
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "carCost",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 60,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "transit",
                        "coef": -8
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "walkability",
                        "coef": -0.3
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "education",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "schoolQual",
                        "coef": 0.9
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "school",
                        "coef": 2
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "healthcare",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "hospitalQual",
                        "coef": 0.9
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "hospital",
                        "coef": 2
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "groceryAccess",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "groceryQual",
                        "coef": 0.8
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "grocery",
                        "coef": 4
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "groceryCost",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 0,
                    "min": 0,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "tally": "groceryCostAvg",
                        "coef": 1
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "field": "happiness",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 50,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "field": "education",
                        "coef": 0.15
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "healthcare",
                        "coef": 0.15
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "groceryAccess",
                        "coef": 0.15
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "walkability",
                        "coef": 0.1
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "park",
                        "coef": 2
                      },
                      {
                        "tally": "transit",
                        "coef": 1
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "pollution",
                        "coef": -0.3
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "carCost",
                        "coef": -0.15
                      },
                      {
                        "field": "groceryCost",
                        "coef": -0.4
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ],
                "history": {
                  "table": "city_history",
                  "copy": [
                    "turn",
                    "budget",
                    "population",
                    "happiness"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "glmap",
            "table": "parcels",
            "latColumn": "lat",
            "lonColumn": "lon",
            "labelColumn": "zone",
            "zoom": 14,
            "height": 420,
            "styleUrl": "https://www.openhistoricalmap.org/map-styles/main/main.json",
            "action": {
              "fn": "editRow"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "style": "caption",
            "value": "Basemap: OpenHistoricalMap (historical style) on web; desktop falls back to a standard map. The rules are plain JSON in the End-turn button — open Edit mode to tune the model."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "stats": {
      "title": "City stats",
      "body": {
        "type": "column",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "style": "caption",
            "value": "Residents' happiness and what drives it. End turns to grow the city; watch the trends."
          },
          {
            "type": "table",
            "table": "city",
            "columns": [
              "happiness",
              "education",
              "healthcare",
              "groceryAccess",
              "groceryCost",
              "walkability",
              "carCost",
              "pollution"
            ],
            "height": 96
          },
          {
            "type": "piechart",
            "table": "parcels",
            "groupColumn": "zone",
            "label": "Parcels by zone",
            "height": 170,
            "colors": {
              "residential": "blue",
              "commercial": "purple",
              "industrial": "gray",
              "park": "green",
              "grocery": "amber",
              "school": "teal",
              "hospital": "red",
              "transit": "pink"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "barchart",
            "table": "residents",
            "groupColumn": "band",
            "label": "Residents by mood"
          },
          {
            "type": "linechart",
            "label": "Happiness over turns",
            "table": "city_history",
            "xColumn": "turn",
            "yColumn": "happiness",
            "height": 170
          },
          {
            "type": "linechart",
            "label": "Population over turns",
            "table": "city_history",
            "xColumn": "turn",
            "yColumn": "population",
            "height": 170
          },
          {
            "type": "linechart",
            "label": "Budget over turns",
            "table": "city_history",
            "xColumn": "turn",
            "yColumn": "budget",
            "height": 170
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "residents": {
      "title": "Residents",
      "body": {
        "type": "column",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "style": "caption",
            "value": "Every resident has their own happiness, driven by what's physically NEARBY. A line-of-sight proxy (proximity within a radius) checks how much real-world nature/parks they can reach, how much road/car exposure they suffer, and their access to groceries, schools and hospitals. Each factor is weighted by that resident's own nature and car preferences — nature-lovers gain more from nearby green, the car-averse lose more next to roads. The green/road points are real OpenStreetMap features baked into this app."
          },
          {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "Recompute happiness",
            "icon": "calculate",
            "action": {
              "fn": "spatialScore",
              "args": {
                "subjects": "residents",
                "latColumn": "lat",
                "lonColumn": "lon",
                "factors": [
                  {
                    "name": "natureF",
                    "table": "features",
                    "column": "kind",
                    "value": "green",
                    "radiusMeters": 300
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "parkP",
                    "table": "parcels",
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "park",
                    "radiusMeters": 300
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "carF",
                    "table": "features",
                    "column": "kind",
                    "value": "road",
                    "radiusMeters": 200
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "indP",
                    "table": "parcels",
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "industrial",
                    "radiusMeters": 300
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "grocery",
                    "table": "parcels",
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "grocery",
                    "radiusMeters": 400,
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "school",
                    "table": "parcels",
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "school",
                    "radiusMeters": 500,
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "hospital",
                    "table": "parcels",
                    "column": "zone",
                    "value": "hospital",
                    "radiusMeters": 600,
                    "agg": "avg",
                    "field": "quality"
                  }
                ],
                "effects": [
                  {
                    "field": "happiness",
                    "mode": "set",
                    "base": 50,
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 100,
                    "terms": [
                      {
                        "factor": "natureF",
                        "prefField": "naturePref",
                        "coef": 6
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "parkP",
                        "prefField": "naturePref",
                        "coef": 8
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "carF",
                        "prefField": "carTolerance",
                        "coef": -5
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "indP",
                        "coef": -4
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "grocery",
                        "coef": 0.1
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "school",
                        "coef": 0.1
                      },
                      {
                        "factor": "hospital",
                        "coef": 0.1
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ],
                "bandField": "band",
                "bandFrom": "happiness",
                "bands": [
                  {
                    "max": 40,
                    "name": "low"
                  },
                  {
                    "max": 70,
                    "name": "ok"
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "high"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "glmap",
            "table": "residents",
            "latColumn": "lat",
            "lonColumn": "lon",
            "labelColumn": "name",
            "colorColumn": "band",
            "colors": {
              "low": "red",
              "ok": "amber",
              "high": "green"
            },
            "zoom": 14,
            "height": 420,
            "styleUrl": "https://www.openhistoricalmap.org/map-styles/main/main.json",
            "action": {
              "fn": "editRow"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "cards",
            "table": "residents",
            "title": "name",
            "subtitle": "happiness",
            "emptyIcon": "groups",
            "emptyTitle": "No residents yet",
            "emptyText": "Once your city has people, recompute happiness to see how each resident feels about their neighborhood.",
            "sort": {
              "column": "happiness",
              "dir": "desc"
            },
            "tags": [
              {
                "column": "band",
                "colors": {
                  "low": "red",
                  "ok": "amber",
                  "high": "green"
                }
              }
            ],
            "action": {
              "fn": "editRow"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "guide": {
      "title": "How to play",
      "body": {
        "type": "column",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Goal: maximise residents' happiness while staying solvent."
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "style": "caption",
            "value": "Zones & effects:\n• Residential — adds population.\n• Commercial / Industrial — earn budget (industry pollutes).\n• Grocery — set its Quality and Cost; high quality + low cost lifts happiness.\n• School / Hospital — set Quality → education / healthcare.\n• Park — happiness, walkability, less pollution.\n• Transit — raises walkability, cuts car cost and pollution.\n\nEach End turn: budget changes by your mix; population grows from housing; pollution, walkability, car cost, education, healthcare, grocery access & cost recompute; and happiness = a weighted blend of all of them. People, cars and transit are modelled as these factors (not animated). Tune every number in Edit mode — the rulebook is JSON."
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
